div.span: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Speed by one stage.

Causes the target to fall in love with the user, giving it a 50% chance to do nothing each turn. If the user and target are the same gender, or either is genderless, this move will fail. If either Pokémon leaves the field, this effect ends.

div.div: Orcafin loves frolicking in the sunlit waters of lakes! It can mesmerize foes with its bubble attack & lure them with its attractive powers.
